        "text": " love of the brethren, and in your love of the brethren, charity.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " In other words, your godliness must not be selfish and solitary, but social and Christian; for he who loveth God must love his brother also (",
        "children": []
