      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1John 4:20-21",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). And though “charity begins at home” with “them who are of the household of faith,” it must not end there, but reach out to all men, whether Christians or not. (Comp. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1Thessalonians 3:12",
        "children": []
